stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> RequestSent : Submit email
    RequestSent --> TokenGenerated : Valid email
    RequestSent --> Error : Invalid email
    Error --> Idle
    TokenGenerated --> LinkClicked : User clicks email link
    LinkClicked --> NewPasswordEntered : Enter new password
    NewPasswordEntered --> PasswordUpdated : Token valid
    NewPasswordEntered --> TokenExpired : Token invalid
    TokenExpired --> Idle
    PasswordUpdated --> [*]